      "content": "i get that, but my nephrologist is actually super hard to reach and i don't have an appointment for another two weeks. the headache is getting pretty bad and it's making it hard to focus on work. is it really that risky if i just take one or two standard dose ibuprofen pills just to get through the afternoon? i feel like a little bit won't hurt much.",
